@Alias(value={"str","STR"})
public class SortTileRecursiveBulkSplit
extends AbstractBulkSplit
    Sort-Tile-Recursive aims at tiling the data space with a grid-like structure for partitioning the dataset into the required number of buckets. Reference:

    Leutenegger, S.T. and Lopez, M.A. and Edgington, J.:
    STR: A simple and efficient algorithm for R-tree packing
    In: Proc. 13th International Conference on Data Engineering, 1997
